  "description": "<p>此外有谣传称微软将会在2014年推出不带Kinect的Xbox One游戏主机，不过微软的回应可能会让这些抱有期待的消费者失望了。根据最新的报道正微软并没有计划将Kinect和Xbox One分离单独出售。<strong>微软“相信”Kinect和Xbox One搭配能够提供最佳的使用体验，才能充分发挥游戏主机的强悍性能，并且主机上的包括语音命令等一些功能都是通过Kinect进行扩展衍生的。</strong><br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2f2b81dc/sc/21/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246103.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%ABKinect%E7%9A%84Xbox+One%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246103.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%ABKinect%E7%9A%84Xbox+One%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246103.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%ABKinect%E7%9A%84Xbox+One%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246103.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%ABKinect%E7%9A%84Xbox+One%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246103.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4