  "description": "<p><strong>鉴于有15%的用户会通过手机来访问维基百科，因此该网站绝对为该在线百科全书提供在途编辑的选项。</strong>上周三，维基百科推出了一项新功能，以便可以让用户在智能手机或平板电脑上编辑文章。更重要的是，任何人可以在任何时刻的任何地点编辑这款免费的在线百科全书，而无需选定的某组编辑的权限。因此，移动集成势必大大简化用户编辑的流程。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2f2b81d8/sc/2/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246102.htm&amp;t=%E6%94%BE%E5%BC%80%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%B4%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246102.htm&amp;t=%E6%94%BE%E5%BC%80%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%B4%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246102.htm&amp;t=%E6%94%BE%E5%BC%80%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%B4%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246102.htm&amp;t=%E6%94%BE%E5%BC%80%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%B4%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\